  "text": "Today is the day!! Easy Everyday is out in the world and I am SO excited! The book is available everywhere that books are sold. You can order online at: Where To Buy Get a SIGNED COPY HERE from Penguin Bookshop!!! Amazon Barnes \u0026 Noble Bookshop.org Books A Million Target Hudson Booksellers Apple Ebook Google Play Ebook  I am so, so excited for you to get your hands on this book. And I want to hear from you! Tell me everything. What recipe are you most excited about? What are you looking forward to cooking?! The 10-minute meal prep strategy is how the entire book comes together. All of the recipes have meal prep tips and I share lots of strategies on feeding your family in an enjoyable way, removing the stress and chaos! Inside the book, you’ll find my everyday essentials – think dressings, sauces and all the quick recipes I keep in my fridge to make dinner come together quickly. These things elevate meals and bring so much versatility throughout the week. Tons of meatless recipes. Snacks, desserts, drinks and everything in between. We are going to have so much fun cooking through it. You can join the cookbook club to cook through it with us! Thank you so much for your amazing support over the years! Be sure to tag me on instagram @howsweeteats and tag everything you’re making with #howsweeteats! Remember, I can only see your account if it’s public! I want to be able to feature your amazing creations. Post a picture of your copy of Easy Everyday! I can’t wait to hear what you think about the book. Shoot me an email, leave me a comment, leave a review, send me a DM – whatever is your preferred way of contact. Love you so much! xoxoxo",
